&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Tbilisi?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-tbilisi" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-tbilisi" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://daytrips.techpawz.com/posts/tbilisi-day-trips/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Tbilisi&lt;/a&gt;, the capital of &lt;a href="https://daytrips.techpawz.com/posts/tbilisi-day-trips/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Georgia&lt;/a&gt;, is a vibrant city that effortlessly blends a rich history with an eclectic modern culture. Nestled in the picturesque valleys of the Caucasus Mountains, Tbilisi boasts stunning architecture that ranges from medieval churches to contemporary art installations. The city&amp;rsquo;s diverse heritage is evident in its cobblestone streets, where ancient fortresses sit alongside chic cafes and art galleries. As you wander through the Old Town, the charm of Tbilisi&amp;rsquo;s colorful houses with their ornate wooden balconies will captivate you.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>